  {name: "[正妹] 日本新生代演員 - 濱邊美波", content: "\n嗨～熱愛櫻花血統女孩兒的我又來了\n\n這次介紹的女孩—濱邊美波\n\n濱邊美波（Minami Hamabe），2000年出生（你沒看錯…2開頭出生的已經被我們送進口袋\n名單了），備受矚目的未來女星。\n\n先上寫真照\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/uLufGum.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/uLufGum.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/uLufGum.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\n日本網友：\n拜託不要長歪！\n她一個比全部AKB漂亮\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/xA0fEDR.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/xA0fEDR.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/xA0fEDR.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\n擁有令人忘記呼吸的凝人氣質，回想起呼吸後吸進的第一口氣如此清晰純淨\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/5rD1yI3.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/5rD1yI3.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/5rD1yI3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\n以下劇照\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/dbapczD.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/dbapczD.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/dbapczD.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\n媽我戀愛了\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/U7draKn.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/U7draKn.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/U7draKn.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\n日劇未聞花名\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/qznYP9d.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/qznYP9d.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/qznYP9d.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fppHYqa.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/fppHYqa.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/fppHYqa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/RKDZU4W.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/RKDZU4W.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/RKDZU4W.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n人美做什麼都美，挖鼻孔一定也超正\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/8KJQX0J.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/8KJQX0J.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/8KJQX0J.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\n\n以上！\n其實挺意外沒有在板上搜尋到濱邊美波\n\n有機會再介紹高能櫻花妹吧！\n\n--\n<span class=\"f2\"></span>", user_id: nil, avatar_file_name: nil, avatar_content_type: nil, avatar_file_size: nil, avatar_updated_at: nil, type_id: nil, cover_image: nil, ptt_post_id: "M.1450973201.A.C5B", ptt_post_link: "https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Beauty/M.1450973201.A.C5B.html"},
  {name: "[神人] LUXGEN S3車展SG", content: "\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/uGMEyEh.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/uGMEyEh.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/uGMEyEh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>在車版看到 小弟的菜\n\n覺得甜美已戀愛\n\n不知道有沒有人認識她?\n\n\n--\n<span class=\"f2\"></span>", user_id: nil, avatar_file_name: nil, avatar_content_type: nil, avatar_file_size: nil, avatar_updated_at: nil, type_id: nil, cover_image: nil, ptt_post_id: "M.1450985488.A.0A9", ptt_post_link: "https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Beauty/M.1450985488.A.0A9.html"},
