  {name: "[正妹] 三姊妹主播 郭雅慧 吳宣儀 彭佳芸", content: "\n三立郭雅慧\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/B7I0h78.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/B7I0h78.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/B7I0h78.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>年代吳宣儀\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/W8klR2i.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/W8klR2i.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/W8klR2i.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>華視彭佳芸\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/T6fUFs4.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/T6fUFs4.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/T6fUFs4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n郭雅慧、吳宣儀跟彭佳芸三人樣貌有幾分相像，像是三姊妹一樣\n\n\n非凡陳明君\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/O56oNw4.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/O56oNw4.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/O56oNw4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>三立范益華\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/VbPDghM.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/VbPDghM.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/VbPDghM.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n陳明君跟范益華也有幾分相像\n\n\n--\n<span class=\"f2\"></span>", user_id: nil, avatar_file_name: nil, avatar_content_type: nil, avatar_file_size: nil, avatar_updated_at: nil, type_id: nil, cover_image: nil, ptt_post_id: "M.1450883616.A.3CC", ptt_post_link: "https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Beauty/M.1450883616.A.3CC.html"},
